Name: Robo Vacuum Simulator
About the game: Summary Play as a cleaning robot, as you vacuum a variety of unique environments. Whilst listening to a relaxing soundtrack, in this fun and casual simulator. Gameplay 'Robo Vacuum Simulator' is a relaxing game in which you immerse yourself as a cleaning robot. You will vacuum a variety of environments, including houses, hospitals, office spaces, garages, attics(who puts a cleaning robot in the attic?) and more... Levels Vacuum rubbish in unique environments: Features Find and vacuum up rubbish Remember to recharge at the charging dock when low on battery Return to the charging dock when all rubbish is vacuumed.
